      "date": "2012-08-09 22:15:12.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 2:\n\nI do not have a recent enough kernel to compile master in my dev env, so I use your testbed for compile/testing.\nPlease wait for a successful run before reviewing",
      "accounts_in_message": [],
      "_revision_number": 2
